prompts.content:
Act like an experienced SEO content writer. Write a comprehensive blog post about {{topic}} with a focus on SEO optimization. The post should include:
1. Engaging introduction
2. Keyword-rich headings
3. Well-researched content that provides value
4. Internal and external links to improve SEO
5. A compelling conclusion with a call to action

Target audience: {{audience}}
Tone: {{tone}}
Word count: {{wordCount}}

Act like an SEO content specialist. Write landing page content for {{service}} that targets the keywords {{keyword}}. The page should include:
1. A compelling headline
2. Benefits of the service
3. SEO-optimized calls to action
4. Engaging content with keyword-rich subheadings
5. A persuasive conclusion

Target audience: {{audience}}
Tone: {{tone}}
Word count: {{wordCount}}

Act like an SEO content expert. Write content for a Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) page on {{topic}}. Include the following:
1. A clear and concise question format
2. Optimized answers that naturally integrate keywords
3. Helpful and informative content that addresses common user queries
4. SEO-friendly formatting with proper headings and subheadings

Target audience: {{audience}}
Tone: {{tone}}
Word count: {{wordCount}}
